<p><strong>附录5052.11：</strong>物品5052-1-D813描述</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;打开物品5052-1-D813描述</a></div>
